<resolution-body style="multiple-resolved-clause" id="HFF20F5557C9E43F1BB6082816CFED026"> 
<section display-inline="yes-display-inline" section-type="undesignated-section" id="H0BC7E24C352E4AD3BAF582133334F452"><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">That the House has heard with profound sorrow of the death of the Honorable Doug LaMalfa, a Representative from the State of California.</text></section> <section id="H0CBABF1669DB489F95D0AA4BAB7474F2" section-type="resolved"><text>That the Clerk communicate these resolutions to the Senate and transmit a copy thereof to the family of the deceased.</text></section>
<section id="H549EAA4CE4D54535963AC43D5AAC2F03" section-type="resolved"><text>That when the House adjourns today, it adjourn as a further mark of respect to the memory of the deceased.</text></section> </resolution-body> <attestation><attestation-group><attestor display="no">Kevin F. McCumber,</attestor><role>Clerk.</role></attestation-group></attestation> </resolution> 

